Package cdm.product.template

Interface EquityPayout

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.rosetta.model.lib.GlobalKey, PayoutBase, com.rosetta.model.lib.RosettaModelObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    EquityPayout.EquityPayoutBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EquityPayout.EquityPayoutBuilderImpl, EquityPayout.EquityPayoutImpl
    @RosettaClass
public interface EquityPayout
extends PayoutBase, com.rosetta.model.lib.GlobalKey
    The equity payout specification terms. The associated globalKey denotes the ability to associate a hash value to the EquityPayout instantiations for the purpose of model cross-referencing, in support of functionality such as the event effect and the lineage.
    Version:
    2.119.0
